def: The bill or beak of a bird; the neb.
The act of individualizing; the state of being individualized;individuation.

p. p. of Swear. Sworn brothers, originally, companions in armswho took an oath to share together good and bad fortune; hence,faithful friends.-- Sworn enemies, determined or irreconcilable enemies.-- Sworn friends, close friends.
A bollard timber. See under Bollard.
Of or pertaining to Siam, its native people, or their language.
A four-stroke cycle, as the Otto cycle, for an internal-combustion engine. -- Four"-cy`cle, a.
One who inoculates; one who propagates plants or diseases byinoculation.
Of or pertaining to the millennium, or to a thousand years; as,a millennial period; millennial happiness.
That branch of pharmacology which considers the mode of action,and the effects, of medicines. Dunglison.
